function AmbushTarget()

	local tPlayers = Hydra.PlayerActors()
	
	local tValidTargets = {}
	for iter, idPlayer in pairs(tPlayers) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idPlayer) then
			table.insert(tValidTargets, idPlayer)
		end
	end
	
	ShuffleTable(tValidTargets)
	
	return tValidTargets[1]
end

function HordeTrigger()

	local idAmbushLocation = AmbushTarget()
	Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(S_SPAWNER_AMBUSH, idAmbushLocation, true, 4, 8, Hydra.MR_NORMAL, Hydra.PowerSNOFromName(Hydra.ReferencePower("Summoned_Animating_Ceiling")))
	
end

function ExecutionerTrigger()
	
	local idAmbushLocation = AmbushTarget()
	Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(S_SPAWNER_EXECUTIONER, idAmbushLocation, true, 4, 8, Hydra.MR_ELITE, Hydra.PowerSNOFromName(Hydra.ReferencePower("Summoned_Animating_Ceiling")))

end
